Test RFP Document for AI Chatbot Implementation

This document outlines the requirements for implementing an AI-powered chatbot system.

Data Processing Requirements:
- Process customer personal data including names, emails, support tickets
- Customer interactions stored and analyzed for service improvement
- Integration with existing customer database systems

Security Requirements:
- Secure authentication mechanisms required
- All data transmissions must be encrypted
- Regular security audits must be conducted

AI Implementation:
- Machine learning algorithms for response accuracy
- Bias detection and mitigation capabilities required
- Regular model updates and monitoring needed

Compliance Requirements:
- Must comply with GDPR requirements
- Customer data processing following privacy regulations
- Incident reporting procedures must be established
